Recorded January/February 2008 in Tepotzlán, Morelos, Mexico at Valle Místico.

Released in a gatefold cover with printed inner-sleeve. Two stickers on the outer plastic wrapper: A big silver one by Merge Records about the MP3 download and claiming "Hi-Quality 180 Gram Vinyl For Maximum Sound Quality".
Plus a smaller clear sticker "Conor Oberst - A new solo album from Conor Oberst Of Bright Eyes".

This LP release came with a code to download an MP3 version of the album from Merge Record's website.

All track lengths for this LP are taken from the track lengths of those downloaded MP3s.
